claim: Adolf Hitler did not lead the Nazi regime.
premise_source_doc_sentence: Adolf Hitler  (  -LSB- ˈadɔlf ˈhɪtlɐ -RSB- ; 20 April 1889 -- 30 April 1945  )  was a German politician who was the leader of the Nazi Party  (  Nationalsozialistische Deutsche Arbeiterpartei ; NSDAP  )  , Chancellor of Germany from 1933 to 1945 , and Führer  (  `` Leader ''  )  of Nazi Germany from 1934 to 1945 .
